channel.title: My First Phat!
channel.description:
Well I just got one! I've spent ages trying to get one and I'll tell you how, It's really easy! Here is me getting it:
[img]http://img291.imageshack.us/img291/1426/finalui5.gif[/img] (It's in a loop so it turns back again :D :D)
I thought I might of needed the knife but I didn't, Sorry it's a bit fast. And You can add any dye to it to colour it!
Yes it's old but I like it :P
